Dialogue: 1,0:00:01.58,0:00:02.34,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:01.58,0:00:02.34,Transcription_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,皆さん、こんにちは。
Dialogue: 3,0:00:01.58,0:00:02.34,Romanized_1_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,minasan、 konnichiha。
Dialogue: 1,0:00:03.02,0:00:06.26,Transcription,,0,0,0,,This is a demo of a new tool called WhisperSub.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:03.02,0:00:06.26,Transcription_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,これは、WhisperSubという新しいツルのデモです。
Dialogue: 3,0:00:03.02,0:00:06.26,Romanized_1_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,koreha、 WhisperSub toiu atarashii tsuru no demo desu。
Dialogue: 1,0:00:07.10,0:00:09.64,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Using this tool, you can extract audio from MKV files
Dialogue: 2,0:00:07.10,0:00:09.64,Transcription_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,このツルを使えば、mkbファイルから
Dialogue: 3,0:00:07.10,0:00:09.64,Romanized_1_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,kono tsuru wo tsukae ba、 mkb fairu kara
Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.64,0:00:13.06,Transcription,,0,0,0,,automatically, perform transcription,
Dialogue: 2,0:00:09.64,0:00:13.06,Transcription_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,自動的に音声を抽出し、文字起こし
Dialogue: 3,0:00:09.64,0:00:13.06,Romanized_1_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,jidouteki ni onsei wo chuushutsu shi、 moji oko shi
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.06,0:00:16.34,Transcription,,0,0,0,,and merge subtitles.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:13.06,0:00:16.34,Transcription_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,を行い、そして字幕を結合することができます。
Dialogue: 3,0:00:13.06,0:00:16.34,Romanized_1_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,wo okonai、 soshite jimaku wo ketsugou surukotogadekimasu。
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.26,0:00:19.42,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, it supports multiple languages
Dialogue: 2,0:00:17.26,0:00:19.42,Transcription_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,さらに、複数の言語に対応
Dialogue: 3,0:00:17.26,0:00:19.42,Romanized_1_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,sarani、 fukusuu no gengo ni taiou
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.42,0:00:21.62,Transcription,,0,0,0,,and can automatically convert to romanized
Dialogue: 2,0:00:19.42,0:00:21.62,Transcription_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,していて、ロマ字兵の変換も自
Dialogue: 3,0:00:19.42,0:00:21.62,Romanized_1_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,shiteite、 roma ji hei no henkan mo ji
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.62,0:00:23.96,Transcription,,0,0,0,,text, making it very convenient.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.62,0:00:23.96,Transcription_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,動で行えるので、とても便利です。
Dialogue: 3,0:00:21.62,0:00:23.96,Romanized_1_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,dou de okonae runode、 totemo benri desu。
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.70,0:00:26.60,Transcription,,0,0,0,,It can also process noisy audio
Dialogue: 2,0:00:24.70,0:00:26.60,Transcription_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,ノイズが多い音声でも処理でき
Dialogue: 3,0:00:24.70,0:00:26.60,Romanized_1_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,noizu ga ooi onsei demo shori deki
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.60,0:00:29.34,Transcription,,0,0,0,,as it includes voice separation functionality.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:26.60,0:00:29.34,Transcription_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,るように、音声分離の機能も備えています。
Dialogue: 3,0:00:26.60,0:00:29.34,Romanized_1_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,ruyouni、 onsei bunri no kinou mo sonae teimasu。
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.49,0:00:31.06,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Please give it a try.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.49,0:00:31.06,Transcription_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,ぜひ試してみてください。
Dialogue: 3,0:00:29.49,0:00:31.06,Romanized_1_1_Transcription,,0,0,0,,zehi tameshi temitekudasai。
